DESCRIPTION:How to Read a Poem: \\nJoin us on Wednesday\\\, March 25 from 7
	-9 p.m. in the Hugo House salon for a reading from ten local poets: Brian 
	Giddens\\\, Diane Qi\\\, Jay French\\\, Laura Titzer\\\, Margaret O’Donnel
	l\\\, Mariko Navin\\\, Mark Onnen\\\, Meg Hofer\\\, Mike Nadal\\\, and Wen
	dy Roach. Hosted by Jeanine Walker. Free to attend.\n\nhttps://hugohouse.o
